Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:02.87,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}いざ征け 光あれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.09,0:01:12.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}KNIGHTS KNIGHTS KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA Ah Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:18.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}KNIGHTS KNIGHTS KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA Ah Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:36.28,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}星間に行く砦は唯一の安息地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:42.37,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}焦燥に打ち震え 所以には生と死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:47.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}KNIGHTS KNIGHTS KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA Ah Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:53.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}KNIGHTS KNIGHTS KNIGHTS OF SIDONIA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:02:01.01,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}此所へいざ集わんと 導かれしは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:07.30,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}志携えて 立ち向かえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:13.70,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}衛り継ぐ愛と 輝け命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:21.66,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}果敢に進む我ら シドニアの騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:02.87,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}踏上征途 光芒与我们同在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:36.28,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}穿梭星际的堡垒是唯一的安息之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:42.37,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}颤抖因焦躁而激发 生死于因果中存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:02:01.01,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}齐聚此地 接受引导
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:07.30,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}众志成城 携手迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:13.70,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}满怀薪火相传的爱与灿烂的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:21.66,OP_CHS,,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}希德尼娅的骑士果敢前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:36.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}あぁ 朽ちていく世界ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:40.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}散りゆく運命ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:45.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}何を信じて生きればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:51.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}そう 君と出逢わなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.23,0:22:54.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}この胸を引き裂くような
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:23:00.63,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}痛みなんて知らなかったから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.96,0:23:05.33,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}空の彼方 鳴り響いた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:08.56,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}拙い鎮魂歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:08.56,ED,NTP,80,0,0,,{\be1\fs20}レクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:12.71,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}それでもまだ探している
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:15.80,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}不確かな現実から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:15.80,ED,NTP,95,0,0,,{\be1\fs20}いま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.28,0:23:18.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}君のことを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.19,0:23:21.75,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}巡り逢えた歓びも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:25.48,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}消えていった温もりも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:29.73,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}ねぇ 全部覚えてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.00,0:23:32.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}愛してたから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:36.53,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}芽生えていく感情も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.73,0:23:40.30,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}胸に残る傷跡も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.38,0:23:44.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}ねぇ 全部抱えて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.78,0:23:51.38,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}この道を歩いて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:36.43,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}倘若世界将要腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:40.00,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}如果注定难逃死灭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:45.00,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}此生究竟该相信什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:51.00,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}是的 如果不曾与你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.23,0:22:54.70,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我便不必体会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:23:00.63,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}这撕心裂肺的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.96,0:23:05.33,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}响彻在宇宙彼岸的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.67,0:23:08.56,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}是那稚拙的镇魂之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:12.71,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:15.80,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}依然从飘乎的现实中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.28,0:23:18.15,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}找寻你的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.19,0:23:21.75,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}相逢的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:25.48,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}消散的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:29.73,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我都历历在目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.00,0:23:32.77,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}因为曾经深爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:36.53,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}萌生的情愫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.73,0:23:40.30,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}残留的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.38,0:23:44.45,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我都铭记在心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.78,0:23:51.38,ED_CHS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}一路前行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.26,0:00:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袋状结构破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探测不到任何奇居子的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融合个体要不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认融合个体䌷仍然存活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇居子刚才对我做了非常过分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让它们对我的朋友和同伴做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷 希格斯粒子密度上升
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！䌷！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.65,0:00:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷 听话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科户濑机 严重损毁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇550的希格斯粒子密度急剧上升
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.39,0:00:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轨道在与䌷和科户濑机的接触点发生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来人 去救䌷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.92,0:00:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷 䌷她…！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融合个体整备班 至岐神开发厂区特殊培养槽集合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船员医疗班 火速救治受伤的卫人操纵士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重伤者送往高度紧急治疗室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻伤者送往医务局第三科或中央医院
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜 拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岐神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷 䌷她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在丧失了90%的身体组织
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会把䌷恢复原样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前出击并回舰的机体中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前约有50%已完成整备并运回机库待命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个融合个体又救了我们一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有她 我们肯定已经无家可归了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎玛莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次真是好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼娅和你都没事真是万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弦打——！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死性不改
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才打了那么场恶战啊 你就少计较点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来 没想到你换成了义肢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是坚决啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是奶奶建议的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为组织再生要花很多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手脚你很快就能适应的 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还方便得很
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你挺精神的 我也放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候可以出院？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不说我了 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷还没恢复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&HC99DCF&}给䌷姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&HC8A789&}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&HC8A789&}保护了希德尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H978FC9&}祝你能赶快好起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢她的人有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.79,0:06:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比之前好一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转换炉管的第1024次定期清扫将按时进行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次清扫…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想快点向䌷道谢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.46,0:07:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说战斗口粮换新了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去试吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那艘移民舰是在放出先遣队后返航希德尼娅的途中遇袭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能有人顺利到达七号行星就已经不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在大众合船正在逼近雷姆星系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就够了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来很累的样子 估计是没怎么睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风他累了或者身体不舒服了也从来不说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他的这一点很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也反而让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前也认识一个和长道很像的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以常常很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在看到他一个人承担太多东西的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是长道一定不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他一个人待一阵子 很快就会振作起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风长道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.54,0:09:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天也来看望䌷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷已经移到通常培养槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胞衣已经基本上完全复原 只等恢复意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.94,0:09:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吃相太难看了啦 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？星…白…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星 白…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一不小心睡着了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看上去睡得很香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷 谷风先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,䌷！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那 你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:11:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 听说你醒了 我就把它带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我可以摸摸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要温柔一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,软软的 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:29.01,eyecatch,NTP,1020,0,0,,希德尼娅百景　无人小摊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:32.02,eyecatch,NTP,950,0,0,,希德尼娅百景　外周壁连接桥内部通道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前希德尼娅与大众合船所在的位置之间隔着恒星雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们处于对方的死角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为按照计划进入雷姆星系 本舰将开始减速
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 继续保持警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融合个体的情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在为外壳设置了专用的房间 让她在其中待命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.27,0:13:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现有武器再加上䌷也还是敌不过大众合船的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长是另有妙计吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过上一场战斗 融合个体反对派的势力已经大幅削弱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个东西怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就将进入第一次启动实验
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我转告由蕾博士 我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 能看到外面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像比之前的房间大了一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢看书 所以小一点也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷风先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是觉得这里离居住区有点远
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才开始就一声不吭的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我就是在刚才的䌷身上看到了一个人住在地下的她的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 去拜托缬让䌷能够进入居住区嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 进来一下说不定还是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来现在重力就已经不稳定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是发生事故怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都给我差不多一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 别走那么快啊 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是这个洞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 从管理局那边拿到的地图上也是这么标的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 又是这么黑漆漆的路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 出血了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啊 长道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我没事 赶紧往前走吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼娅正面喷射口 已打开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让工作队撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航向 行星九号的卫星轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备反向喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反向喷射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发布重力警报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼娅现在将开始反向喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请将安全带扣在安全扶手上 准备迎接冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼娅现在将开始反向喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请将安全带扣在安全扶手上 准备迎接冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道 刚才是不是有什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差一点了 再加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:16:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反向喷射 准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.18,0:17:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面第一、第二喷射口 点火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始反向喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种振动是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 说起来今天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喷射已稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重力场发生装置及平衡即将恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要 要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长道 到外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了 就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:19:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是居住塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.37,0:20:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那整栋建筑里住着很多人是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那里有好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.45,0:20:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那么多人 肯定也有很多种生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能变成人类的大小
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去很多地方 结识很多人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.82,0:20:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该有多棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们每个人都知道你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没想过能亲眼见到这样的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的东西怎么会在走廊上…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:21.67,Default,NTP,150,0,0,,{\an7}谷风长道先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}今天是新训练生入住的日子，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}但是您的物品还未整理完毕。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}因此我们将其放到了门外。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}请见谅。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}希德尼娅军总务科
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不能再住宿舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我可不是在跟你说笑话啊 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你比计划的要慢 所以我一直很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 义肢也需要调整呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 有人来电了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 那我先挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:21:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再见 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长 长道 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 突然找你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天能让我住一晚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.05,0:22:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.64,0:22:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶——？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
